[gd_resource type="Theme" load_steps=18 format=3]

; StarReach base theme — dark navy palette, gold/cyan accents, portrait-readable.
; Applied at the root Control of main_menu and main_screen; modals inherit
; via Godot's theme cascade. No custom font yet — Godot's default handles
; Hangul + Latin at 720×1280 legibly. Swap in Noto Sans KR when art passes.

